<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>Lead Quality Dashboard</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>
<style>:root{--bg:#f5f4f0;--surface:#fff;--surface1:#f8f7f4;--border:rgba(0,0,0,.09);--border-s:rgba(0,0,0,.16);
--text:#0b0b0b;--sec:#52514e;--muted:#898781;--blue:#2a78d6;--teal:#1baf7a;--amber:#ba7517;
--red:#e34948;--gray:#73726c;--r:8px}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){:root{--bg:#111110;--surface:#1c1c1a;--surface1:#252522;
--border:rgba(255,255,255,.09);--border-s:rgba(255,255,255,.16);--text:#f5f4f0;--sec:#c3c2b7;
--muted:#898781;--blue:#3987e5;--teal:#199e70;--amber:#eda100;--red:#e66767;--gray:#888780}}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5}
.page{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1.25rem 4rem}
.dash-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-bottom:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem}
.dash-header h1{font-size:20px;font-weight:500}
.dash-header p{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}
.kpi-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:2rem}
.kpi{background:var(--surface);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:.9rem 1.1rem}
.kpi-lbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:6px}
.kpi-val{font-size:26px;font-weight:500;line-height:1}
.kpi-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--sec);margin-top:4px}
.kpi-target .kpi-val{color:var(--amber)}
.grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(400px,1fr));gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
.card{background:var(--surface);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1.1rem 1.25rem}
.card-t{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:1rem}
.cw{position:relative;width:100%}
.filter-bar{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.5rem;background:var(--surface);border:.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:.8rem 1rem;align-items:center}
.filter-bar label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-right:4px}
select{font-size:12px;padding:3px 8px;border:.5px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--surface1);color:var(--text);cursor:pointer}
.filter-grp{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px}
.tabs{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1rem}
.tab{padding:4px 12px;border-radius:var(--r);border:.5px solid var(--border-s);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;color:var(--sec)}
.tab:hover{background:var(--surface1)}
.tab.on{background:var(--blue);color:#fff;border-color:var(--blue)}
.hbar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:6px}
.hbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--sec);width:165px;flex-shrink:0;text-align:right;line-height:1.3}
.hbt{flex:1;background:var(--bg);border-radius:3px;height:19px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hbf{height:100%;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-left:5px;transition:width .3s ease}
.hbp{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap}
.hbn{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);width:54px;flex-shrink:0}
.sc-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.sc-lbl{width:255px;flex-shrink:0;font-size:11px;color:var(--sec);line-height:1.4}
.sc-lbl span{display:block;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)}
.sc-track{flex:1;background:var(--bg);border-radius:3px;height:23px;position:relative;overflow:visible}
.sc-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end;padding-right:6px}
.sc-pct{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:#fff}
.sc-mark{position:absolute;top:-4px;bottom:-4px;width:2px;background:var(--amber);z-index:2;border-radius:1px}
.insight{background:#eaf3de;border:.5px solid #97c459;border-radius:var(--r);padding:.7rem .9rem;margin-top:.9rem;font-size:12px;color:#27500a;line-height:1.6}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){.insight{background:#173404;border-color:#3b6d11;color:#c0dd97}}
.dl{font-size:11px;color:var(--sec);line-height:2}
.dl-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.dl-sq{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0}
.note{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.6rem}
footer{margin-top:3rem;padding-top:1rem;border-top:.5px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem}</style></head><body>
<div class="page">
<div class="dash-header"><div><h1>Lead quality dashboard</h1><p>One publisher · 3,021 leads · generated server-side, no public data link</p></div><span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)">Generated 6/29/2026, 10:23:59 AM</span></div>
<div class="kpi-row">
<div class="kpi"><div class="kpi-lbl">Total leads</div><div class="kpi-val" id="k-total">—</div></div>
<div class="kpi"><div class="kpi-lbl">Closed rate (baseline)</div><div class="kpi-val" id="k-closed">—</div><div class="kpi-sub" id="k-cn">—</div></div>
<div class="kpi"><div class="kpi-lbl">Broad quality rate</div><div class="kpi-val" id="k-good">—</div><div class="kpi-sub">closed + EP steps</div></div>
<div class="kpi kpi-target"><div class="kpi-lbl">CPL uplift target</div><div class="kpi-val">9.6%</div><div class="kpi-sub">+20% → $33 CPL</div></div>
</div>
<div class="filter-bar">
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--sec);margin-right:4px">Filter:</span>
<div class="filter-grp"><label>Partner</label><select id="f-partner"><option value="">All</option></select></div>
<div class="filter-grp"><label>Debt level</label><select id="f-debt"><option value="">All</option></select></div>
<div class="filter-grp"><label>Month</label><select id="f-month"><option value="">All</option></select></div>
<div class="filter-grp"><label>State</label><select id="f-state"><option value="">All</option></select></div>
<button id="reset-btn" style="margin-left:auto;font-size:12px;padding:3px 10px;border:.5px solid var(--border-s);border-radius:var(--r);background:transparent;color:var(--sec);cursor:pointer">Reset filters</button>
</div>
<div class="grid2">
<div class="card"><div class="card-t">Closed rate by month</div><div class="cw" style="height:195px"><canvas id="trendChart"></canvas></div></div>
<div class="card"><div class="card-t">Status breakdown</div><div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
<div class="cw" style="height:170px;width:170px;flex-shrink:0"><canvas id="donutChart"></canvas></div>
<div class="dl" id="donut-legend"></div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1.25rem">
<div class="card-t">Segment analysis</div>
<div class="tabs" id="seg-tabs"><button class="tab on" data-seg="partner">Traffic source</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="trafficType">Search vs Display</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="widget">Ad creative</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="adGroup">Ad group / keyword</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="debt">Debt level</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="phone">Phone score</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="addr">Address score</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="state">Geography</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="campaign">Ad campaign</button>
<button class="tab" data-seg="landingPage">Landing page</button></div>
<div id="seg-body"></div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1.25rem">
<div class="card-t">Q3 — paths to 9.6% quality target</div>
<div class="note">Computed from the full dataset each time this dashboard loads; not affected by the filters above (filtering to one partner and then asking "how do I improve on this partner" isn’t a meaningful question).</div>
<div id="scenario-body"></div>
</div>
<footer><span>Source: server-side read of the configured Google Sheet (not publicly published)</span></footer>
